<section class="content-section">
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>I live in the UK in rural Oxfordshire with my wife, daughter and our cat, not far from where I grew up</p>
  <p>With a full stack engineering background, I am currently Principal SRE at <a href="https://360insights.com">360 Insights</a></p>
  <p>I specialise in designing and building robust, secure and scalable application hosting platforms, mainly on AWS</p>
  <p>I have worked with object orientated code for well over 10 years, in numerous languages, mostly PHP and Ruby, to build applications, websites and APIs of various kinds.</p>
  <p>A linux user since 1999 and Open Source advocate, I enjoy helping people learn about web technology and passing on useful skills and best practice</p>
